Despite the ‘noise’ accompanying the long and intense political season in 2017, the year still lent itself to the traditional dichotomy of Best and Worst Communication Moments.  We, therefore, invite you to make your submissions of the Best and Worst Communication Moments of 2017, which will be published upon compilation by our team of applied and academic communication experts. Click here for the entry form. Submission deadline: December 29, 2017. 
 